                        <interp inst="t18380820-name-237" type="given" value="JOHN GKOROE"></interp>JOHN GKOROE HOFFMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a tailor, and live at Duke-street, St. James's. The prisoner was my foreman—I thought it necessary to send for a policeman—he searched his coat pocket in my presence, and this lines was found—it had no business in his pocket.</p>
